Today We Making Some Sweet & Spicy Vegan.. Well Vegetarian (sorry a bitch be high) Chicken with Rice & Brussels sprouts, Here’s the Ingredients or What Ever.

Vegan Chicken:
From “Sweet Earth” .. But any plain / grilled vegan “chicken” would work fine too! 

Marinade:
Honey 
Brown Sugar 
Soy Sauce 
Minced Garlic 
Ginger 
Sriracha Sauce 
Crush Red Pepper Flakes 
(don’t use too much of last 2 ingredients if you don’t like spicy shit) 
Add A Tbs of Water if it’s too thick!

Rice:
I Used “Better Than Rice” you can find it at one of them bougie organic health food stores in your area or buy the shit Amazon! 
You can use Regular White Rice Also

Brussel sprouts:
watch the video cause I’m tired of typing how

- Cin 💕

So I said moving forward I’m going to be posting different type of content alongside of my comedy videos, instead of making multiple pages (don’t nobody have time for that shit 😭) Here’s A Workout I Did This AM, As Time Progresses I’ll add in more exercises etc, but for Now here’s What I’ve been doing 10 , 1 Mins Sprints on the Treadmill (because I absolutely HATE running) • Followed By 5 Sets Of Abs on the Exercise Ball & Since Today Was Leg Day I Choose 3 Different Types Of Lower Body Exercises I Do 5 Sets / 12-15 Reps Each. I Like To Keep It Simple I Believe In Consistency, Not Over working & killing myself. 
We About 2 Weeks In, I’ll Be Posting Before & Afters Soon! Follow The Progress💦✨

node.text:
I Hate The Music They Play 😩😭 
Let Me Connect My Phone 🤣
.
.
.
#hiphop #rap #car #comedy

To all of my OG followers, you guys know that Fashion has always been my First Love! 

Contrary to popular belief, I never really was interested in women’s wear though. Last year durning the panicmic things changed for me. the whole world was on pause, and all that alone time gave me time to be creative, play with different  ideas and explore women’s wear.  I’m not going to lie it was a bore at first 😭 my creative juices weren’t flowing at all. I kept at it and finalIy designed my first collection. Entitled “Wearable Art” I wanted to play with simple ideas and add my twist to it all while incorporating ideas stemmed from some of my favorite contemporary artistes 🖼 
[ cc: @thechellegirlofficial ]

It’s been a long ride, countless sleepless nights dealing with production who run on total different time zones, ideas not coming out how you envision them and having to scrap them completely, being consistently indecisive and having to finalize designs, the whole nine. 

I want to thank my team , family & friends who continued to push me and had to deal with all my mood swings during this process! 🥴😅🧡If you haven’t already MAKE SURE YOU FOLLOW MY BRAND PAGE 👉🏽 @thechellegirlofficial & TURN ON YOUR POST NOTIFICATION 🔔 

DROP 1.
Releases Early Next Week! 
Prices Range $60-250
Very Limited Quality So Make Sure Your Post Notifications Are On 

this is only the beginning more collections, [@thechellegirlofficial] more dopest and more to come 🤞🏾
